Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Profile

  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates the employee Profile object. The profile includes the name, department, and dateHired of the employee. The methods used in this class are toString(), equals(), getName(), dateToString(), getDepartment(), getDateHired().
    Author:
    Jasmin Kaur, Jonathan Delin
